column4:
So this is the family tree of Esau, ancestor of the people of Edom, in the hill country of Seir. The names of Esau’s sons:
Eliphaz, son of Esau’s wife Adah;
Reuel, son of Esau’s wife Basemath.

Zebulun settles down on the seashore;
he’s a safe harbor for ships,
right alongside Sidon.

Benjamin is a ravenous wolf;
all morning he gorges on his kill,
at evening divides up what’s left over.
